#: ../../cxflow/portal-publishing.md:35
msgid "Portal Features"
msgstr "포탈 기능"

#: ../../cxflow/portal-publishing.md:37
msgid ""
"**Document tree** — left sidebar with folder-grouped navigation (JS: "
"`tree.js`)"
msgstr ""
"**문서 트리** — 폴더 그룹 탐색이 있는 왼쪽 사이드바 (JS: `tree.js`)"

#: ../../cxflow/portal-publishing.md:38
msgid ""
"**Table of contents** — auto-generated from Markdown headings (JS: "
"`toc.js`)"
msgstr ""
"**목차** — Markdown 헤딩에서 자동 생성 (JS: `toc.js`)"

#: ../../cxflow/portal-publishing.md:39
msgid "**Markdown rendering** — `html_cache` displayed with portal-specific CSS"
msgstr "**Markdown 렌더링** — 포탈 전용 CSS로 `html_cache` 표시"

#: ../../cxflow/portal-publishing.md:40
msgid "**Responsive layout** — works on desktop and tablet"
msgstr "**반응형 레이아웃** — 데스크톱과 태블릿에서 작동"

#: ../../cxflow/portal-publishing.md:42
msgid "Change Request Portal"
msgstr "변경 요청 포탈"

#: ../../cxflow/portal-publishing.md:44
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Issues with `issue_type=change_request` get a portal URL at "
"`/my/cxflow/cr/{id}`, allowing customers to review and approve CRs "
"directly."
msgstr ""
"`issue_type=change_request`인 이슈는 `/my/cxflow/cr/{id}`에서 포탈 URL을 "
"받아 고객이 직접 변경 요청을 검토하고 승인할 수 있습니다."

#: ../../cxflow/portal-publishing.md:47
msgid "Publisher — PDF / DOCX Export"
msgstr "퍼블리셔 — PDF / DOCX 내보내기"

#: ../../cxflow/portal-publishing.md:49
msgid ""
"The `lu_cxflow_publisher` module provides a full publishing pipeline with"
" configurable style profiles."
msgstr ""
"`lu_cxflow_publisher` 모듈은 설정 가능한 스타일 프로필을 갖춘 전체 "
"배포 파이프라인을 제공합니다."

#: ../../cxflow/portal-publishing.md:52
msgid "Publish Profiles"
msgstr "배포 프로필"

#: ../../cxflow/portal-publishing.md:54
msgid ""
"A publish profile (`lu.cxflow.publish.profile`) defines the output "
"styling:"
msgstr ""
"배포 프로필 (`lu.cxflow.publish.profile`)은 출력 스타일을 정의합니다:"

