#: ../../cxflow/portal-publishing.md:84
msgid "Quick Publish"
msgstr "빠른 배포"

#: ../../cxflow/portal-publishing.md:86
msgid ""
"Each document has one-click **Publish PDF** and **Publish DOCX** buttons "
"that use the `customer` profile. The generated file is attached to the "
"document and a download action is returned."
msgstr ""
"각 문서에는 `customer` 프로필을 사용하는 원클릭 **Publish PDF** 및 "
"**Publish DOCX** 버튼이 있습니다. 생성된 파일은 문서에 첨부되며 "
"다운로드 액션이 반환됩니다."

#: ../../cxflow/portal-publishing.md:90
msgid "Batch Publishing"
msgstr "일괄 배포"

#: ../../cxflow/portal-publishing.md:92
msgid "For larger exports:"
msgstr "대규모 내보내기의 경우:"

#: ../../cxflow/portal-publishing.md:94
msgid "Go to **CxFlow → Publishing → Jobs**"
msgstr "**CxFlow → Publishing → Jobs**로 이동"

#: ../../cxflow/portal-publishing.md:95
msgid "Create a new job, select the profile and scope"
msgstr "새 작업을 생성하고 프로필과 범위를 선택"

#: ../../cxflow/portal-publishing.md:96
msgid "Optionally filter by state (`all` or `approved` only)"
msgstr "선택적으로 상태로 필터링 (`all` 또는 `approved`만)"

#: ../../cxflow/portal-publishing.md:97
msgid "Click **Run**"
msgstr "**Run** 클릭"

#: ../../cxflow/portal-publishing.md:99
msgid ""
"When multiple documents are exported with `both` format, the publisher "
"creates a ZIP bundle containing all generated files."
msgstr ""
"여러 문서를 `both` 형식으로 내보내면 퍼블리셔가 생성된 모든 파일을 포함하는 "
"ZIP 번들을 생성합니다."

#: ../../cxflow/portal-publishing.md:102
msgid "Job States"
msgstr "작업 상태"

#: ../../cxflow/portal-publishing.md:114
msgid ""
"Partial failures are handled — if some documents succeed and others fail,"
" the job moves to `done` with the successful attachments available."
msgstr ""
"부분 실패가 처리됩니다 — 일부 문서가 성공하고 다른 문서가 실패하면 작업은 "
"성공한 첨부 파일을 사용할 수 있는 상태로 `done`으로 이동합니다."

#: ../../cxflow/portal-publishing.md:117
msgid "Dependencies"
msgstr "의존성"

#: ../../cxflow/portal-publishing.md:119
msgid "**PDF**: requires `wkhtmltopdf` installed on the server"
msgstr "**PDF**: 서버에 `wkhtmltopdf` 설치 필요"

#: ../../cxflow/portal-publishing.md:120
msgid "**DOCX**: requires `python-docx` Python package"
msgstr "**DOCX**: `python-docx` Python 패키지 필요"
